flowchart TD
    START([Session Start\n4:00 ET]) --> LOAD[Load 3m Bars\nOvernight + Session]
    LOAD --> FVG[Detect All FVGs\nfrom overnight + RTH bars]
    FVG --> INDICATORS[Calculate Indicators\nEMA 20/50, ADX 14, DI+/DI-]

    INDICATORS --> ENTRY_A{Entry Type A\nCreation}
    INDICATORS --> ENTRY_B{Entry Type B\nRetrace}
    INDICATORS --> ENTRY_C{Entry Type C\nBOS + Retrace}

    ENTRY_A --> COLLECT[Collect All Valid Entries\nSort by Bar Index]
    ENTRY_B --> COLLECT
    ENTRY_C --> COLLECT

    COLLECT --> LOOP[/For Each Bar in Session/]
    LOOP --> MANAGE[Manage Active Trades\nTrail Updates + Exit Checks]
    MANAGE --> GATES{Entry Gates}

    GATES -->|Pass| SIZE[Position Sizing\n3 cts / 2 cts / 1 ct]
    GATES -->|Fail| LOOP

    SIZE --> OPEN[Open Trade\nEntry + Stop + Targets]
    OPEN --> LOOP

    LOOP -->|EOD 16:00| EOD[Close All Remaining\nat Market Close]
    EOD --> SUMMARY([Print Results])
